metatags.twitter:description: This year, the Dulles Plane Pull is going VIRTUAL! You can “pull” with us from the comfort of your own home for the first time! The event will occur virtually during the week of October 12. Join us for a fitness competition Monday - Friday then celebrate with us on Saturday, October 17, our Virtual Dulles Plane Pull day. Each team will be connected with a SOVA athlete coach to be motivated by and train unified with along the way and will have the opportunity to participate in three team contests!
